OL,3,CVolunteers helping thousands of toads
OL,4,Ccross the road safely
OL,6,FA road will be closed for the next six
OL,7,Fweeks to allow toads, frogs and newts
OL,8,Fto cross to their breeding grounds.
OL,10,FThe Charlcombe Toad Rescue Group is
OL,11,Fhoping to help more than 3,000
OL,12,Famphibians reach their ancestral
OL,13,Fbreeding lake in the valley below.
OL,15,FCharlcombe Lane near Bath, Somerset,
OL,16,Fwill be shut until March 25 as
OL,17,Fvolunteers go out on patrol each night
OL,18,Fat dusk to help common toads, common
OL,19,Ffrogs and newts on their journey.
