OL,3,CVolunteers helping thousands of toads
OL,4,Ccross the road safely
OL,6,FIt was the second-best year for the
OL,7,Fnumber of amphibians recorded and the
OL,8,Fbusiest in 14 years.
OL,10,FLast year also saw the largest number
OL,11,Fof newts helped on record and it was
OL,12,Fthe best for toads since 2013.
OL,14,FThe annual closure has taken place
OL,15,Feach spring since 2003 with the
OL,16,Fagreement of Bath and North East
OL,17,FSomerset Council.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
