OL,3,CVolunteers helping thousands of toads
OL,4,Ccross the road safely
OL,6,FIt is only one of four road closures
OL,7,Fin the UK and it has played a vital
OL,8,Frole in keeping the local population
OL,9,Fof amphibians stable during the last
OL,10,F20 years.
OL,12,FBefore the closure of Charlcombe Lane,
OL,13,Fthe casualty rate was 62% while in
OL,14,F2024 it was 6%.
OL,16,FHelen Hobbs, who has been managing
OL,17,FCharlcombe Toad Rescue Group since
OL,18,F2003, said: "Closing Charlcombe Lane,
OL,19,Fwith the support of the local
OL,20,Fcommunity, has been a game changer for
OL,21,Four amphibian population.
