OL,3,CVolunteers helping thousands of toads
OL,4,Ccross the road safely
OL,6,F"It has meant that toads, frogs and
OL,7,Fnewts have been able to buck national
OL,8,Ftrends and stand a fighting chance of
OL,9,Fflourishing.
OL,11,F"With a changing climate it is
OL,12,Fbecoming increasingly difficult to
OL,13,Fpredict the peak times for amphibian
OL,14,Fmovements, which is why closing the
OL,15,Froad for six weeks really matters.
OL,17,F"Last year the busiest period was
OL,18,Fearly February and in 2023 it was mid-
OL,19,FMarch."
