OL,3,CVolunteers helping thousands of toads
OL,4,Ccross the road safely
OL,6,FIn 2016 a team of scientists used data
OL,7,Fcollected by toad patrols to explore
OL,8,Fwhat had been happening to the
OL,9,Fpopulation of common toads across the
OL,10,FUK.
OL,12,FThe research demonstrated that the
OL,13,Fcommon toad population had declined by
OL,14,F68% in just 30 years.
OL,16,FThe biggest challenges facing
OL,17,Famphibians include road traffic, loss
OL,18,Fof habitat, such as the disappearance
OL,19,Fof ponds, and the fragmentation of
OL,20,Fhabitats due to the intensification of
OL,21,Ffarming and development.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
