OL,4,Ccross the road safely
OL,6,FA changing climate is also adversely
OL,7,Faffecting amphibians, with milder
OL,8,Fwinters leading to them waking up from
OL,9,Fhibernation more frequently.
OL,11,FThere are more than 200 patrols across
OL,12,Fthe UK helping amphibians during the
OL,13,Fmigration season.
